<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customer Care - Bank of America</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #0033a0; 
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        .navbar-left .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar-right {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px; 
        }

        .navbar-right .nav-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-right .nav-link:hover {
            color: #ffc72c; 
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #0070c9;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        ul li {
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }

        .phone {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }

        .d {
            font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .form-container {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .form-container input, .form-container select {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .form-container button {
            width: 84%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #0070c9;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .form-container button:hover {
            background-color: #005bb5;
        }
        .fade-out {
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .fade-in {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sections {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .sections {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        .error-message {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Light transparent red */
    color: darkred; /* Dark red text */
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px; /* Small border radius */
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: normal;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out forwards, shake 0.5s ease-in-out 0.5s;
}
.success-message {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: rgba(0, 255, 17, 0.1); /* Light transparent red */
    color: rgb(37, 143, 19); /* Dark red text */
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px; /* Small border radius */
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: normal;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out forwards, shake 0.5s ease-in-out 0.5s;
}
/* Fade-in effect */
@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

/* Slight shaking effect */
@keyframes shake {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
    25% { transform: translateX(-5px); }
    50% { transform: translateX(5px); }
    75% { transform: translateX(-3px); }
}


    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-left">
            <span class="logo">Bank of America</span>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-right">
            <a href="accdashboard" class="nav-link" onclick="navigateTo('accdashboard')">🏢 Home</a>
            <a href="features" class="nav-link" onclick="navigateTo('features')">✨Features</a>
            <a href="security" class="nav-link" onclick="navigateTo('security')">🔒 Security</a>            
            <a href="aboutus" class="nav-link">ℹ️About Us</a>            


        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>📞 Customer Care Service</h1>
        <p>
            At <b>Bank of America</b>, we are committed to providing top-notch customer support. Our customer service team is available <b>24/7</b> to assist you with banking queries, account management, and fraud protection. Feel free to contact us for any help! 😊
        </p>

        <h2>🌟 Features of Our Customer Care Service</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>📅 <b>24/7 Support:</b> We are available anytime to assist you.</li>
            <li>💳 <b>Card Assistance:</b> Report lost or stolen cards immediately.</li>
            <li>🔒 <b>Fraud Protection:</b> Secure your account from unauthorized access.</li>
            <li>🏦 <b>Account Management:</b> Get help with transactions and statements.</li>
            <li>📧 <b>Email & Chat Support:</b> Connect with us via multiple channels.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>☎️ Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            📞 <b>Customer Service Number:</b> <span class="phone">+91-9003563788</span>
        </p>

        <h3 class="d">For Any Other Problem, Provide Your Details</h3>

        <!-- Customer Service Form -->
        <div class="form-container">
            <form action="" method="POST">
                {{#if errorMessage}}
    <p class="error-message"> {{errorMessage}} </p>
{{/if}}
                {{#if successMessage}}
    <p class="message success-message">{{successMessage}}</p>
{{/if}}


                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                <input type="text" name="accnum" placeholder="Account Number" required>
                <input type="number" name="phno" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
                
                <select name="pt" required>
                    <option value="">Select Problem Type</option>
                    <option value="credit_debit_issue">💰 Amount Credit/Debit Problem</option>
                    <option value="account_balance">📊 Account Balance</option>
                    <option value="fraud">🚨 Fraud Amount Debit</option>
                    <option value="lost_card">💳 Lost Card</option>
                    <option value="login_issue">🔑 Login/Create Account Problem</option>
                    <option value="other">📝 Other</option>
                </select>

                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        function navigateTo(page) {
            const sections = document.querySelector('.sections');
            sections.classList.add('fade-out');
            setTimeout(() => {
                window.location.href = page;
            }, 300);
        }
</body>
</html>
